¶ Living and a working
on the land

01:18:04.175 --> 01:18:06.837
¶ La-la la-la-la la-la

01:18:07.011 --> 01:18:11.220
¶ La-la-la la-la la-la

01:18:11.391 --> 01:18:16.977
¶ La-la-la la-la la-la la

01:18:17.146 --> 01:18:22.482
¶ Living and a-working
