01:25:00.633 --> 01:25:03.124
¶ Let my love open the door

01:25:03.302 --> 01:25:06.009
¶ When everything
feels all over

01:25:06.180 --> 01:25:08.796
¶ Everybody seems unkind... ¶

01:25:08.974 --> 01:25:12.307
Ladies and gentlemen, if you
would please take a seat.

